<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ʿd ạlsạʿạt</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ- ʿd ạlsạʿạt ạlly ạnt qḍythạ wạlạwqạt ạlly fyhạ frḥt

[V2]
 sẖwf km mrẗ ḥsyt sʿạdthạ wkạm mrẗ fyhạ ḥznt

[V3]
 sẖwf qd ạyẗ sʿạdtk ạtsbbtlk fy ạlqywd

[V4]
 sẖwf qd ạyẗ kẖlt ṭryq ạlḥyạẗ qdạmk msdwd

[V5]
 wlạn ʿdwk msẖ ʿạyz ywṣlk gẖyr llmwt

[V6]
 ạlqrạr - ạyẗ ạḥly mn ạlwqt ạlly tqḍyẗ qdạm ạllh

[V7]
 ạlhk ạlly byḥbk wạdạlk ạlḥyạẗ

[V8]
 wạlly rjwʿk lyẗ sẖỷ dạymạaⁿ bystnạh

[V9]
 2- ʿd ạlạwqạt ạlly ḍạʿt mnk mn gẖyr qymẗ whdf ạw ḥlm

[V10]
 sẖwf ạlḥạlẗ ạlly bqt fyhạ nfsk mn gẖyr mạykwn ʿndk ʿlm

[V11]
 sẖwf qd ạyẗ kl ạlly sẖạyfạh ʿynyk qdạmk jnwn

[V12]
 mṭrwd mn gẖyr mạ ykwn ṭạrd wbtbʿd ʿn ạllh ạlḥnwn

[V13]
 wlạn ʿdwk msẖ ʿạyzk tʿysẖ gẖyr mhzwm

[V14]
 3- ạlbrkẗ wạllʿnẗ ạtnyn qdạmk wạnt ạlly dạymạaⁿ tkẖtạr

[V15]
 yạ tʿysẖ ḥyạtk fy rḍạ ạlhk yạ tʿysẖhạ mʿ ạblys fy ạlnạr

[V16]
 sẖwf myn ạlly ḥbk ʿlsẖạn ynqdẖk mn ạlmwt

[V17]
 wạtrk ṭryq ạlḍʿf ạlly ạnt dạymạaⁿ fyẗ btmwt

[V18]
 ạrjʿ lạlhk ạlly gẖlb ʿlsẖạnk ạlmwt</lyrics>
<author>ʿạdl ḥbyb, ʿạdl ḥbyb</author>
<hymn_number>10372</hymn_number>
</song>